Backout Plan
+++++++++++++++++++++


Switches -

Hostname				IP address

202-FR-SWA024-L2-DT21B	10.255.56.24
202-FR-SWA073-L2-DT11	10.255.56.73

SSH To Access Switch

Config t

no errdisable recovery cause loopback
no errdisable recovery cause bpduguard
no errdisable recovery cause psecure-violation
no errdisable recovery cause udld
no errdisable recovery cause link-flap
no errdisable recovery cause storm-control
no errdisable recovery cause pagp-flap
no errdisable recovery cause channel-misconfig

Config t
interface <Gig1/0.x>
no spanning-tree portfast
no spanning-tree bpduguard enable


Step 3 - 

Remove Additional Standard Configuration [Access Ports ]


no storm-control broadcast level 10.00
no storm-control multicast level 15.00
no storm-control action shutdown

30 mins
